member.summary:
Indicate which delete mode can be applied on this conversation when call delete_conversation method. 
1:only support soft-delete mode; 
2:only support hard-delete mode; 
3:support both soft-delete mode and hard-delete mode. 
Default is 3 if this field is missing.

